Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add Vitest test suite with 43 tests covering API routes (teams, skills,
  gap-analysis, register) and core lib (skill-gap.ts)
- Add GitHub Actions CI workflow (lint, type-check, test, build)
- Add multi-stage Dockerfile and docker-compose.yml for local dev
- Standardize error handling across all 24 API routes via handleApiError()
- Add global error boundary (src/app/error.tsx)
- Fix TypeScript linting: empty interface to type alias in input/textarea
- Fix unescaped apostrophe in invite-member-dialog
- Downgrade react-hooks/set-state-in-effect to warn for data-fetch pattern
